,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T04:17:53.000Z","msg":"朝早起身: J 連迪路夫紋身圖 <br />\n早餐食紅雞蛋，一條心，撐紅魔！ <br />\n睇番98/99三冠王珍藏版dvd，拎定三卷tempo廁紙，以防睇到歐聯反勝階段走火 <br />\n<br />\nlunch搭水晶觀光巴士食lunch<br />\n慶祝今季脫離大巴足球，食一餐贏一場，聯賽38連勝指日可待 <br />\n<br />\n下午剪新髮型扮普巴，練琴扮山齊士，開電腦J碧咸/費格遜/蘇斯克查/雲佩斯<br />\n<br />\nJ完換曼聯(作客)波衫落街，買架雪佛蘭(曼聯sponsor)，揸到扯扯地。 <br />\n<br />\n晚飯係全日重點，著住全套曼聯波衫波褲，手持Manchester United F.C 頸巾，去尖沙咀Manchester United Restaurant Bar，大唱會歌共20202020次，20字=20次英超聯聯冠軍。 <br />\n<br />\n晚上安然跳上曼聯床單睡床，準備夢見全隊曼聯職球員夢遺！"},{"pid":"4808d018ba46de68bd8060223c9118fd5b2c1212","tid":966644,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T04:22:47.000Z","msg":"意假咁都好意思抽人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c83be9f4fa9874e7805866f86fa635989ea25c63","tid":966644,"uid":53238,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T04:26:12.000Z","msg":"19 年先 4 年<br />\n4 年 3 冠 wo<br />\n數字都唔識數 ?"},{"pid":"68ad4716ad7f055792841492499da5ccf63f1aa9","tid":966644,"uid":23385,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d177b143fd1e5e92f9a3ab089b046d6c7a924379","tid":966644,"uid":166474,"like":57,"dislike":2,"score":55,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T03:13:50.000Z","msg":"高普鍾意儲亞軍獎牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T04:27:18.000Z","msg":"高普同小花咪天作之合<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e60e983adafbcfccafa4840d0f6c2029eb838f1c","tid":966644,"uid":155137,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T04:29:10.000Z","msg":"祖記唔係AC踢 根本冇辦法証明自己"},{"pid":"78b8fca4d8a0e1dbd051047d827ca2b08abb4bf6","tid":966644,"uid":155137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T04:29:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>祖記唔係英超踢 根本冇辦法証明自己</blockquote>"},{"pid":"df37012d4346cb277f065c78d19e5c9add44756c","tid":966644,"uid":35365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-03T04:29:51.000Z","msg":"屌帥有個意甲係幫ac贏"},{